Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Peace prize for Sanchez
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440ftc
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Oct 1987
Peace prize award to Costa Rican president is a slap in the face for Contra-supporting Reagan. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less